<img class="alignright wp-image-47 size-medium" src="http://harryfox.me/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/IMG_6812-225x300.jpg" alt="IMG_6812" width="225" height="300" /></a><a href="http://harryfox.me/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/IMG_6811.jpg"><img class="alignright wp-image-48 size-medium" src="http://harryfox.me/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/IMG_6811-225x300.jpg" alt="IMG_6811" width="225" height="300" /></a> One fine sunny day in Regent\'s Park I drew my ideas for Katy\'s landing page and later the mobile layout for the portfolio page. Unlike the design process for 5 Bad Habits this was extremely brief, but I felt comfortable with the vision I had in my head, with the Bootstrap layout I would use, and with Katy\'s body of work. Aaaaaand I just couldn\'t wait to start coding it.

